270
00:25:56,840 --> 00:25:59,479
You stay on the Park,
eat here, not some coffee shop.

271
00:25:59,680 --> 00:26:01,511
All right.

272
00:26:01,720 --> 00:26:04,951
So I will draw up
the draft agreement tomorrow.

273
00:26:05,160 --> 00:26:09,199
