361
00:33:40,560 --> 00:33:44,235
Honest to God I am. But I was actually
gonna go get something to eat.

362
00:33:44,440 --> 00:33:45,634
So I'll watch it later.

363
00:33:45,840 --> 00:33:49,549
Are you inviting me to dinner,
or are we still mad at each other?

364
00:33:50,880 --> 00:33:52,916
Both.

365
00:34:02,960 --> 00:34:05,030
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

366
00:34:06,720 --> 00:34:09,518
It's a toast to Lewis.

367
00:34:09,720 --> 00:34:12,951
Sweet guy. Loved the animals.
Loved his beer.

368
00:34:13,160 --> 00:34:15,071
- Did he?
- He did.

369
00:34:15,280 --> 00:34:17,475
I never knew that about him.

370
00:34:21,240 --> 00:34:23,435
