407
00:36:55,000 --> 00:36:58,959
- Thanks, Frank. I appreciate it.
- So when did you guys tie the knot?

408
00:36:59,160 --> 00:37:02,470
You know what, Frank?
Get the hell outta here, will you?

409
00:37:05,000 --> 00:37:07,639
- OK?
- Yeah.

410
00:37:07,840 --> 00:37:11,196
- Well, that was fun.
- That was something.

411
00:37:11,400 --> 00:37:14,073
"I'm his wife. " I like that one.
"I'm his wife. "

412
00:37:14,280 --> 00:37:16,840
Thanks. You left this on the table.

413
00:37:19,160 --> 00:37:21,435
- Please watch it.
