414
00:37:23,800 --> 00:37:25,631
Good night.

415
00:38:13,440 --> 00:38:15,078
OK.

416
00:38:20,280 --> 00:38:23,431
<i>OK, Lewis, go ahead.</i>

417
00:38:23,640 --> 00:38:27,553
<i>Um... Hey, guys.</i>

418
00:38:28,880 --> 00:38:31,952
<i>Sheriff. Tony.</i>

419
00:38:35,080 --> 00:38:37,116
<i>Long time, huh?</i>

420
00:38:37,320 --> 00:38:39,197
<i>I guess if you're seeing this tape</i>

421
00:38:39,400 --> 00:38:45,032
<i>you've kind of figured
that my vacation plans... changed.</i>

422
00:38:45,240 --> 00:38:48,277
<i>I was set to go off</i>

423
00:38:48,480 --> 00:38:53,031
<i>and try and save the orang-utan,
do what I can.</i>

424
00:38:56,440 --> 00:38:59,273
<i>Kind of ironic, isn't it?</i>

425
00:38:59,480 --> 00:39:03,871
<i>Look who's caged and...</i>

426
00:39:04,080 --> 00:39:06,116
<i>they say soon to be extinct.</i>

427
00:39:06,320 --> 00:39:09,915
<i>Um... this little docudrama here</i>

428
00:39:10,120 --> 00:39:12,554
<i>was not my idea.</i>

429
00:39:12,760 --> 00:39:14,990
<i>I'm sorry, but, um...</i>

430
00:39:15,200 --> 00:39:19,113
<i>the folks
