431
00:39:19,320 --> 00:39:21,675
<i>have done all they can</i>

432
00:39:21,880 --> 00:39:26,476
<i>and now they tell me
that you guys are my last chance.</i>

433
00:39:26,680 --> 00:39:28,557
<i>So...</i>

434
00:39:28,760 --> 00:39:33,436
<i>I don't know if you're even thinking
about coming back.</i>

435
00:39:33,640 --> 00:39:39,112
<i>But if there's the slightest chance,
