441
00:39:56,400 --> 00:39:59,153
<i>No burgers for you, Sheriff. But, uh...</i>

442
00:39:59,360 --> 00:40:03,239
<i>There's rice. Plenty of rice.
Your rice needs definitely will be met.</i>

443
00:40:03,440 --> 00:40:05,510
<i>But, um...</i>

444
00:40:07,200 --> 00:40:10,476
<i>If you do...</i>

445
00:40:11,440 --> 00:40:13,749
<i>If you do come back,</i>

446
00:40:13,960 --> 00:40:16,349
<i>I will feel guilty, yes,</i>

447
00:40:16,560 --> 00:40:20,348
<i>and... I already do,
just for asking you.</i>

448
00:40:20,560 --> 00:40:22,755
<i>But...</i>

449
00:40:23,920 --> 00:40:27,310
<i>at least I won't feel the fear,
and I know that's not fair.</i>

450
00:40:27,520 --> 00:40:29,397
<i>Um...</i>

451
00:40:29,600 --> 00:40:32,717
<i>so that's why I'm doing this.</i>

452
00:41:15,200 --> 00:41:17,998
- Hey!
- I'm busy!

453
00:41:18,200 --> 00:41:22,432
- Can't take you today.
- Yeah, well, I can't take you either.

454
00:41:32,400 --> 00:41:35,870
Pop, remember that trip I took
a couple of years back, to Malaysia?

455
00:41:36,080 --> 00:41:40,835
Yeah, I remember. Some sleaze was
selling frequent-flyer miles, right?

456
00:41:41,040 --> 00:41:45,352
That's not the point. The point is
this guy is still over there in Penang.

457
00:41:45,560 --> 00:41:48,836
He's kind of a pal.
But anyway, they're gonna hang him.

458
00:41:49,040 --> 00:41:54,797
They found some hashish on him.
But some of the hash was mine.

459
00:41:55,000 --> 00:41:57,150
So if I go back there,

460
00:41:57,360 --> 00:42:01,035
I'd have to serve
three years in prison, Penang Prison.

461
00:42:01,240 --> 00:42:03,276
But if I don't go back,
they hang this guy.

462
00:42:03,480 --> 00:42:06,472
